episodes.title: The 100th Running - Duke Tumatoe
episodes.author: cspangle@bobandtom.com (The BOB & TOM Show)
episodes.summary:
In honor of the 100th Running of the Indianapolis 500 at the Indianapolis Motor Speedway, we are releasing a new CD in cunjunction with Q95 and Penn Station. This playlist includes 14 (in honor of A.J.) bonus tracks we couldn't fit on the disc. Download them now!* 

The album 100 features a brand new song from Duke Tumatoe and some of the greatest BOB & TOM Show race songs and parodies of all time. It is available at all central Indiana Penn Station East Coast Subs locations FREE starting May 9th with the purchase of any Penn Station meal which includes a sub, fry and a drink. Find a location near you at www.PennStation.com

*Some aren't availible for downloading due to copyrights.
